Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Orange County and Real Housewives of Dallas. On OC, the women are still on their trip. Vicki brings up new allegations about Kelly and they finally make amends. On Dallas, the women enter a mud hut and end their trip.


RHOD: 30:52ish
